(48665, 149668, 4473, 1, 'The Perfect Blue (ft. MastaMic)', '在黎明時分，一對情人分手的片段一一浮現', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 2, 'The Perfect Blue\r\n	Painted in the summer rain\r\n	It only appears at the crack of dawn\r\n	Feels like I am here with you\r\n\r\nThe Perfect Blue\r\n	Brings back the greatest pain\r\n	And what I saw, when I looked at you\r\n	I was wrong yet once again\r\n\r\nThe stars have gone away\r\n	My heart sighs it’s too late\r\n	I live my life again\r\n	You fade and you, you fade away\r\n\r\nThe Perfect Blue\r\n	Say hello to summer rain\r\n	Drenched in a song with a melody\r\n	That belongs to you and me\r\n\r\nThe Perfect Blue\r\n	Brings me so close to you\r\n	Tell me, what I''m going to do\r\n	When I say goodbye to me and you\r\n\r\nI smile and smile again\r\n	Hiding my pain and despair\r\n	The laughter and the tears\r\n	You fade and you, you fade away\r\n\r\nRap: \r\n\r\n望住窗外嘅境色\r\n天色係藍色\r\n似曾相識嘅經歷\r\n昔日嘅熟悉\r\n一切回憶已經絕跡\r\n一切你嘅點滴  讓我窒息\r\n得悉你嘅離去為另一個人\r\n枕邊嘅淚印 印證住傷痕\r\n過往嘅枕邊人 到現今陌生人\r\n愛情其實只係呃人嘅蜜運\r\n\r\n為愛我可犧牲\r\n山盟海誓又有幾多會成真\r\n雙人床今日只剩低我一人\r\n嫌我末夠誠心\r\n你會否再關心\r\n可否儘快忘記你\r\n忘記你嘅口味\r\n忘記你嘅氣味\r\n忘記你嘅品味\r\n一切有關你嘅我要忘記\r\n忘記我曾經至愛嘅你\r\n\r\nThe stars have gone away\r\n	My heart sighs it’s too late\r\n	I live my life again\r\n	You fade and you, you fade away\r\n\r\nThe Perfect Blue\r\n	Brings me so close to you\r\n	Tell me, what I''m going to do\r\n	When I say goodbye to me and you\r\n\r\n\r\nRap & Vocal adlib\r\n\r\n不想再相見 我不會再見 不想再見到你一面\r\nSay goodbye to me & you\r\n我與你我都不想再記起\r\n不會相見 不想再記起你\r\nSay goodbye to me & you\r\n只因你我會將你忘記\r\n令我太過傷心 喺你令我太過傷神\r\nSay goodbye to me & you\r\n我唔會珍惜我唔愛我嘅人\r\nSay goodbye to me & you\r\n離開我吧離開我吧\r\nSay goodbye to me & you', '', 291, '', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:05:14', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48666, 149668, 4473, 2, 'Nobody', '當尋找到真愛，我們的心靈就會被釋放', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 4, 'Beam of light shines, from the moonlit skies\r\n	All alone, I''m wondering why\r\n	Standing here, with my heart in my hand,\r\n	Lost in tears, so where to go now?\r\n\r\nI don''t want to be so lost in the world\r\n	Crying for the world to see\r\n	Don''t know what the world has planned, for me\r\n	I hope that someday I will see\r\n\r\n*Nobody knows, what it takes to be free\r\n		To be loved by someone, can it be me?\r\n		Nobody knows, what It takes to be free\r\n		My heart is waiting, set me free.\r\n\r\nThrough the windows of my heart and my soul\r\n	I whisper softly to the wind,\r\n	Wishing, one day, I finally be heard.\r\n	Let my heart sing, I shall receive.\r\n\r\nRepeat *', '', 268, '', 'Skip Moy', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:07:00', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
