(48668, 149668, 4473, 4, 'Generations', 'Generations after Generations...\r\nWhat is it that we all really want?', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 4, 'Generation, after generation\r\n	Nothing really changes that much\r\n	Some still find love\r\n	Some remain unloved\r\n	What is it that everyone wants?\r\n\r\nGeneration, after generation\r\n	Nothing really changes that much\r\n	Some live for love\r\n	Some die for love\r\n	What is it that everyone wants?\r\n\r\n*I don''t want to feel\r\n	So inadequate\r\n	An empty heart in pain\r\n	Without a future\r\n\r\n	Passion is the key\r\n	To one''s identity\r\n	When money comes in between\r\n	Ohh ah...\r\n\r\nGeneration, after generation\r\n	Nothing really changes that much\r\n	Can''t live without love\r\n	Can live without commitment\r\n	What is it that we really want?\r\n\r\nRepeat *\r\n\r\n	What is it that we ALL really want?\r\n', '', 264, '', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:10:30', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48669, 149668, 4473, 5, 'My Soul', 'When two souls entwined \r\nThis is what it sounds like', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 2, 'Your heart understood mine. \r\n		In the depth of the fragrant night, \r\n		I listened with my ravished soul \r\n		To your beloved voice. \r\n\r\nYou are the wind that blows through my heart\r\n		Like water, that runs deep through my veins\r\n		Like the sound of birds that make me smile\r\n		Like the sun that shines within me\r\n', '', 418, '', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:13:07', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48670, 149668, 4473, 6, 'Sweet Little Girl Blue', 'A dream I had when I traveled to Amsterdam.\r\nThe people I met there and the things I''ve seen.\r\nA song about wanting to stay in a dream and never wake up again.', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 2, 'Sweet little girl blue\r\n	Starring at the starry starry night\r\n	She’s dreaming of Amsterdam\r\n	Sipping cold tea from the Netherlands\r\n\r\nHand in hand, walking down the streets\r\n	People dancin’ and smokin’ weed\r\n	She doesn''t care, what everybody’s doing\r\n	She just wants to stay in her dream\r\n\r\nSweet little girl blue\r\n	Starring at the starry starry night\r\n	She’s dreaming of Van Gogh\r\n	Painting pictures of her face and hands\r\n\r\n*Walk the walk, skipping down the streets\r\n	Don''t know who she''s going to meet\r\n	She doesn''t care, what everybody’s thinking\r\n	She just wants to stay in her dream\r\n\r\nRepeat *after solo\r\n\r\nSweet little girl blue\r\n	Starring at the starry starry night\r\n	She''s dreaming of Anne Frank\r\n	Hid away with her in Prinsengracht \r\n\r\nEyes to eyes, smiling as they speak\r\n	People dancin'' and smokin'' weed\r\n	She couldn''t care, why everybody''s watching\r\n	She just wants to stay in her dream\r\n\r\n	Sweet Little Girl blue\r\n	Sweet Little Girl Blue\r\n', '', 225, '', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:14:48', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48671, 149668, 4473, 7, 'You Should''ve Told Me', 'A song about best friends having to say goodbye to one another.', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 4, 'Why do I miss what I''ve never had\r\n	Why does it hurt me so bad\r\n	How can moment turn into sadness\r\n	How can a friendship end like that\r\n\r\nWhy did I do what I did\r\n	I don''t know how to react\r\n	I am wasted and I am sad\r\n	I cannot pick myself up just yet\r\n\r\n*What did I do to deserve this\r\n	I recall your last kiss\r\n	Kiss of death\r\n	You should have told me, you should have told me, before\r\n\r\n	That you''re tired of me\r\n	That you''re sick of my presence\r\n	That you don''t want to see me\r\n	Don''t you know how I feel/I should have known\r\n	You should have told me/But its too late\r\n\r\nWhy do I miss what I''ve never had\r\n	Why does it hurt me so bad\r\n	How can moment turn into sadness\r\n	How can a friendship end like that\r\n\r\nNow you left me with no choices\r\n	But to sulk within my voice\r\n	Intoxicated with the love of my soul\r\n	I cannot pick myself up just yet\r\n\r\nRepeat *\r\n\r\n	You should have told me\r\n	Why oh why, didn''t you tell me\r\n	How could you, how could you not let me know\r\n	Ohhh...You should have told me. (before)', '', 336, '', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:17:00', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48672, 149668, 4473, 8, 'Every now & then', 'Flashbacks of scenes of lovers that can never be together', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 4, 'Let go of the thoughts of you\r\n	I am free to tie my shoes\r\n	Strolling down this memory lane\r\n	Changing every thought again\r\n\r\nI don''t want to see your face\r\n	Haunting me in my refrain\r\n	Catching love songs in my ears\r\n	You appear to be right here\r\n\r\n*Every now & then, I let you out\r\n	Every now & then, I let you howl\r\n	Every now & then, I let you slip in my thoughts \r\n\r\nWalking down this memory lane\r\n	Your shadows I see everywhere\r\n	Reflected through the list of panes\r\n	Hide away from emptiness\r\n\r\nRaindrops down these many drains\r\n	Like the tears that hide my fears\r\n	Catching sad songs in my ear	\r\n	You appear to be right here\r\n\r\nRepeat *\r\n\r\nIf you want to be my friend you know its true\r\n	That our love won''t last, Oh I got no clue\r\n	Telling me you love won''t erase the fact\r\n	That I''m not your girl and you''re not my man\r\n\r\nEvery now & then, I let you out\r\n	Every now & then, I let you howl\r\n	Every now & then, I let you slip in my thoughts \r\n	\r\n		\r\n	Every now & then,	I make you mine\r\n				I make you cry\r\n				I make you wanna fly away\r\n\r\n	Every now & then	I set you free\r\n				I let you be\r\n				I let you be who you wanna be\r\n	\r\n	Every now & then	I let you out\r\n				I let you in\r\n				I let you slip into my heart', '', 285, '', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:18:51', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48673, 149668, 4473, 9, 'A Taste of Life', 'What we taste in life may not be what is right for us', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2012, 30, 0, 4, 'Like wise Baby\r\n 	I am torn\r\n 	In this world of sympathy and pain\r\n	Don’t you see\r\n	Its okay\r\n	Its the sound of Love refrained\r\n\r\nLife’s possession\r\n	We don''t need much\r\n	Just a mess of dust remains\r\n	Drink up darling\r\n	Suck it up\r\n	Give time a chance to get back into place\r\n\r\nThankful for the special moments left behind\r\n	All those anger, fear and joy and tears I tried\r\n	Every step you take gets you closer to the sky\r\n	Welcome to reality\r\n	(A Taste of Life)\r\n\r\nClose your eyes\r\n	Learn to breathe\r\n	Inhale the things you really need\r\n	Make up your mind\r\n	Don’t give up\r\n	Some things are better to remain\r\n\r\nComing into life you came with identity\r\n	All those hopes and dreams & wishes I have plead\r\n	Catch your moment of the truth don’t let it go\r\n	One mistake, and off you go\r\n	(A Taste of Life)\r\n\r\nListen honey\r\n	Wipe your tears\r\n	Heartaches taste like lemon tea\r\n	Can get sour\r\n 	Bittersweet\r\n	Some things are never meant to be', '', 243, '', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:20:27', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
