(48675, 149668, 4473, 10, 'I Don''t Care', 'At the end of the day, being who you are is what its all about', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2000, 30, 0, 4, 'I don’t care\r\n	What you think of me\r\n	This is who I am\r\n	What you get, is what you see.\r\n\r\nI don''t care\r\n	What you feel for me\r\n	The life I want to live\r\n	Is what I want to be\r\n\r\n*Making dreams, or making plans to create\r\n	Living my life, To see, And learning to be-lieve\r\n	I''m not afraid to live my life and feel again\r\n	Taking my strength and hope, I''ll\r\n	Make...It...to the end\r\n\r\nI don''t care\r\n	What you see of me\r\n	I just have to be\r\n	What is best for me\r\n\r\nRepeat *\r\n\r\n', '', 277, '', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:33:12', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48676, 149668, 4473, 11, 'Every now & then (mandarin)', 'Mandarin version of Every now & then', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 2000, 30, 0, 4, '同在一條地平線	來來回回碰不見\r\n給我想你的空間	承諾會不會兌現\r\n\r\n好像忘掉了記憶	曾經記錄每一天\r\n斷斷續續的思念	化成虛無的雲煙\r\n\r\n*	Every now & then, I let you out\r\n	Every now & then, I let you howl\r\n	Every now & then, I let you slip in my thoughts \r\n\r\n\r\n微風輕吹的夏天	忐忑心情沒改變\r\n記得你說過愛情	感覺不到那永遠\r\n\r\n翻開回憶的瞬間	有你走進我心田\r\n空想一遍又一遍  是你給我的訓練\r\n(Repeat * x2)\r\n\r\n徘徊這裡不停的尋找終點	想要把時間	停留在從前\r\n就算你和我走在不同路線	渴望每一天	靠近多一點\r\n\r\noh…oh…oh…\r\n\r\n說聲愛你	好讓你能再浮現\r\n不用懷疑	有時候想你多一點\r\n\r\n(Repeat *)\r\n	\r\nEvery now & then,	 I make you mine\r\n				I make you cry\r\n				I make you wanna fly away \r\nEvery now & then, 	I set you free\r\n				I let you be\r\n				I let you be who you wanna be\r\n(Repeat *)\r\n', '', 286, '', 'AMA 萱寧', 'AMA 萱寧, Johnny Lu', 'AMA 萱寧, Skip Moy, Jezrael Lucero', 'AMA ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-06-02 10:35:05', '2015-03-12 13:52:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
